lead_paragraph: Because of an editing error, an Associated Press article last Sunday about soccer teams that have qualified for next year’s World Cup misstated, in some editions, a step in the process. Eight of the nine second-place UEFA group finishers will qualify for a playoff to determine four spots in the World Cup finals; they will not all qualify.
